Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:08.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演算装置？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:13.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以AIM扩散力场作为媒介构筑成网络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:18.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再通过复数的大脑进行处理从而使复杂代码的演算成为可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是幻想御手的真实面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了进行某个模拟实验而呈递了树形图设计者的使用申请
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:29.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:31.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么被驳回了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:34.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要能够替代的演算装置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这个而对能力者…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经收集了差不多一万人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:43.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该足够用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:47.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别用那么可怕的表情看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快全部都会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:53.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后大家就能解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用于卸载幻想御手的治疗程序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:00:59.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:01.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会留下后遗症
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会恢复正常  不会牺牲任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:11.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.39,0:01:15.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你说这种没有进行过充分临床研究的东西是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是连安慰都算不上嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:19.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺严厉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  没有发现木山春生的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:30.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  将数据查扣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:39.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被摆了一道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经查到这里了么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是失去了和你的联系后才采取行动的话  有点太快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通过其他渠道得知的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:57.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我设置了如果不按特定的顺序来启动器材就会启动保安系统的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来与幻想御手相关的所有数据都丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:02:01.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:04.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够唤醒其使用者的就只剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:06.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的这个程序而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请认真保管好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是木山春生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备员么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:29.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:33.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是只有上面下了命令的时候行动才会迅速的家伙们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将以开发幻想御手的嫌疑者将你拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:39.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻下车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:43.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？ 看来是算总帐的时候了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想御手是通过使用人类的大脑作为演算器的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:55.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但同时  会给使用者带来某种副产物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:03:00.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看件有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把双手放在脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后原地趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人质的少女现在很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实施逮捕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  这不是我想干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  居然是能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用找钱了  请快点逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山正在与警备员交战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:25.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  是在使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:27.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是能力者吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在书库的记录当中没有木山接受过能力开发的记录
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:32.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,328)\fs18}Bank
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很明显是能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看起来好像是多种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:45.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力一个人只能有一种
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有例外的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是幻想御手的原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Level Upper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:06:01.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一万名能力者的神经突触进行联网的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可谓一个巨大的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倘若能将其进行操控就能发生单靠人类的大脑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这一推测是正确的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的木山是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为不可能实现的如同幻想般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重能力者——多重能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:20.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Dual Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警备员居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:27.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:29.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被全歼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:38.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因战斗的余波而昏迷了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对生命没有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:46.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园都市中仅有七人的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:50.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是你也没有碰到过像我这样的对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你  能阻止使用一万人的大脑的我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说「能阻止吗？」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来真的能用数种能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重能力什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:21.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Dual Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:23.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:28.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力  与理论上不可能的那个的方式不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说是  多才能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,328)\fs18}Multi Skilled
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫法什么的无关紧要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我这边的做法是不会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:47.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得我不可能同时使用数种能力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:02.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不顾自己将自己卷进来而使用能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人扫兴  所谓的超能力也就这种程度么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:18.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为把电击击破了就赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:21.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:32.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以住手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想对某件事进行调查而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这个结束了就会解放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:42.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会牺牲任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会牺牲任何人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那么多人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄他人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情怎么可能放任不管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀…虽然是超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究也只是个不谙世事的大小姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:05.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才没资格说我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:10.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们每天所接受的能力开发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:14.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就认为那是安全且有人道的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:21.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园都市的高层隐瞒了对于能力相关的某些重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对此不明真相的教师们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日地对学生的大脑进行着开发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该明白那是多么危险的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.18,0:09:37.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来蛮有趣的话题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:41.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你之后再慢慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我调查吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:47.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空罐！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Graviton
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:00.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  看你该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部…都打飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经完…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为会更难缠些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管埋怨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:45.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用磁力在瞬间形成了盾牌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:52.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零距离的电击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那个笨蛋虽然没奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:58.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便怎样也不会有那种不得了的能力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且已经手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:17.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海里好像直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:20.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:21.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山春生的记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:29.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和木山之间通过电路连接起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:38.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我当教师？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在开什么玩笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:45.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  你持有教师执照的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:46.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  即使拿起教鞭也不足为奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:54.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那只是顺手拿的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:59.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没对你说「离开研究」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:05.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此  我还想把统括理事会相当重视的实验托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被称为留精弃粗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:13.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Child Error
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:18.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为各种原因而被抛弃在学园都市的无家可归的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就是这次实验的被试验者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你所要任教的学生们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想让实验取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要取得被试验者详细的成长数据
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:35.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加以细心的观察并作出相应的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  让你担任他们的班主任不是更加省事么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:43.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:55.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是今天起担任你们的班主任的木山春生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:12.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中计啦  中计啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:14.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:20.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  今天天气不错  稍微晾一下就能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:24.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以在这里换衣服啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们快转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:31.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的飞机场有什么好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞…飞机场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是粗枝大叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:41.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师不怎么受欢迎吧  有男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:46.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话  我来和老师交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爱恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有什么为难的话就告诉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还难以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:17.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是一副很亲近的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不动就缠过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  枝先
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住的公寓就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来洗个澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:45.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是浴缸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:52.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个浴缸值得你那么高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在设施里  一周只能冲两次淋浴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:02.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以向大家炫耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.30,0:15:21.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样的人  要是努力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能够成为大能力者或是超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:26.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:31.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就现阶段来说还无法下定论呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憧憬高等级的能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也有那个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们是由学园都市抚养长大的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.60,0:15:46.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总希望能够为这座都市尽自己的一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:05.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究的时间全泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:21.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌…小孩子…么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是喧闹不止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗枝大叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我的女朋友好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没有礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又爱恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还难以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:46.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  祝您生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食可…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师要做还是能做到的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:21.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有点疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数值上有什么异常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:27.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:29.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:39.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是木山老师的实验嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:47.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮老师算是扮到头了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:52.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多敏值低下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:55.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抗胆碱剂没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起热伤害低容量性冲击更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻注射乳酸林恩凝胶液
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  继续注射的话太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快联络医院
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:11.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌慌张张的  去好好地收集数据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:15.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,针对本次实验  所里已经下达了封口令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.71,0:18:19.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验已经顺利告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:23.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么都没看到  懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:25.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他们有些可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:37.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是科学的发展不可避免的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:42.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把这次的事故放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:46.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还期待你今后的表现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:10.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看到了…么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:34.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么要做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:45.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次实验披着「AIM扩散力场控制的实验」的外皮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:52.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实上却是「用于解析失控能力的规律的诱爆实验」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:57.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过刺激AIM扩散力场来探知失控的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是试验的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:19:59.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:03.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次失控是被事先安排好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:06.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我是后来才发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体…实验…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:14.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子们再也没能睁开双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直沉睡至今
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把他们当作用完就扔的小白鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  要是那样的话  只要通报警备员…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(440,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了寻找能让孩子们康复的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:37.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为了进行事故发生原因的模拟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所申请使用树形图设计者的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:41.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能有树形图设计者的运算能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Tree Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该能够拯救那些孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:52.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就能够再一次在阳光下奔跑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:54.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是申请被驳回了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:56.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整二十三次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统括理事会也是一丘之貉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会让警备员出动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算这样你也不该出此下策…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能救出那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都做得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕与这座城市的所有人为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也休想让我罢手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:23.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:29.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…网络…失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:46.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胎儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:32.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木山的野心将由我来粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.66,0:23:34.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学将由我来拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怪物是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:39.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人告诉我说对手是怪兽啊


